org.openqa.selenium.grid.web

Class ServletRequestWrappingHttpRequest

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.openqa.selenium.remote.http.HttpRequest
      • org.openqa.selenium.grid.web.ServletRequestWrappingHttpRequest
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ServletRequestWrappingHttpRequest

    public class ServletRequestWrappingHttpRequest
extends HttpRequest
    Read-only adapter of HttpServletRequest to a HttpRequest. This class is not thread-safe, and you can only expect to read the content once.
